g%20the%20most%20to%20online%20scammers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d36c49289b805d1db356eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Better%20Business%20Bureau%2C%20people%20aged%2018%20to%2024%20reported%20the%20highest%20median%20losses%20to%20online%20scams%20last%20year.%3Cp%3Eseksan%20Mongkhonkhamsao%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGen%20Z%20reported%20the%20highest%20median%20loss%20to%20scams%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20year%2C%20the%20BBB%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnline%20scammers%20are%20more%20often%20targeting%20younger%20victims%20these%20days%2C%20the%20agency%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20young%20people%20lost%20the%20most%20money%20overall%2C%20boombers%20lost%20the%20most%20to%20romance%20scams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20associate%20online%20scams%20with%20their%20parents%20or%20grandparents%2C%20those%20non-native%20internet%20users%20who%20might%20easily%20fall%20for%20a%20run-of-the-mill%20phishing%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20actually%20the%20generations%20that%20are%20perpetually%20online%2C%20like%20Gen%20Z%2C%20that%20are%20the%20most%20susceptible%2C%20and%20so%20it%20is%20Gen%20Z%20that%20is%20actually%20losing%20the%20most%20money%20%E2%80%94%20by%20far%20%E2%80%94%20to%20online%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbbbmarketplacetrust.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2023-BBBScamTracker-RiskReport-US-040224.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Better%20Business%20Bureau%2C%20people%20aged%2018%20to%2024%20reported%20the%20highest%20median%20dollar%20loss%20on%20average%20to%20scams%20for%20the%20second%20year%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20lost%20%24155%20on%20average%20to%20scams%20in%202023%2C%20with%20most%20of%20the%20money%20going%20to%20rackets%20re