k-investing-strategy-hayes-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenjoy%20a%20strong%20year-end%20surge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reasoning%20that%20the%20bull%20market%20had%20legs.%20The%20chief%20global%20investment%20strategist's%20call%20proved%20to%20be%20eerily%20accurate%2C%20as%20the%20index%20came%20within%20inches%20of%20his%20ambitious%204%2C800%20target%2C%20which%20it%20topped%20a%20few%20weeks%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20has%20changed%20since%20last%20September%2C%20but%20Hayes'%20call%20is%20virtually%20unchanged.%20This%20year's%20early-August%20drawdown%20is%20little%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-year-end-rally-how-to-invest-lerner-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etypical%20seasonal%20turbulence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20his%20view.%20And%20while%20elections%20will%20bring%20more%20market%20swings%2C%20he%20believes%20US%20stocks%20are%20destined%20to%20hit%20new%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20wrote%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndr.com%2Fpublications%2F-%2Fc%2FSP20231205*PDF%2F2024-u-s-outlook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutlook%20for%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20said%20it%20would%20probably%20be%20a%20year%20where%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20couple%20corrections%2C%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20choppy%20sideways%20period%20in%20summer%20and%20mid-year%20going%20into%20the%20fall%20%E2%80%94%20but%20then%20we%20would%20come%20out%20of%20it%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20we'd%20end%20the%20year%20at%20new%20highs%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayes%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20He%20added%20that%20there's%20%26quot%3Bno%20reason%20to%20think%20that%20that's%20not%20still%20the%20higher%20probability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22162c6cfe-0e16-46c0-ade6-70bc03bd9539%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20breadth%20of%20fresh%20air%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20stuck%20in%20place%20for%20the%20second%20half%20of%20August%20after%20a%20powerful%20eight-day-long%20rebound%20that%20erased%20its%20monthly%20losses%2C%20but%20that%20pause%20masked%20a%20major%20market%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20stocks%20in%20aggregate%20took%20a%20breather%2C%20breadth%20improved%20significantly%2C%20Hayes%20said%20in%20a%20late-August%20note.%20A%20greater%20swath%20of%20stocks%20rising%20makes%20for%20a%20healthier%20market%20that's%20less%20reliant%20on%20a%20handful%20of%20large%20companies%2C%20as%20has%20mostly%20been%20the%20case%20since%20the%20start%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHayes%20and%20his%20team%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20market%20concentration%20throughout%20the%20year.%20This%20summer%2C%20the%2010%20largest%20stocks%20made%20up%20a%20staggering%2024%25%20of%20the%20MSCI%20All%20Country%20World%20Index%2C%20which%20was%20the%20highest%20rate%20on%20record%2C%20according%20to%20Ned%20Davis%20Research.%20That%20figure%20has%20fallen%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20to%2022%25%2C%20which%20is%20still%20uncomfortably%20high%20but%20is%20a%20marked%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221450%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Market%20concentration%20NDR%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d20db21d8d2deb96b7d650%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221154%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENed%20Davis%20Research%20(used%20with%20permission)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combination%20of%20concentration%20diminishing%20and%20then%20the%20breadth%20improving%20is%20what%20you%20want%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayes%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20picking%20up%20that%20rotation%2C%20the%20shift%20away%20from%20tech%20into%20other%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20point%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20that%20mega%20caps%20have%20taken%20up%20a%20slightly%20smaller%20share%20of%20global%20markets%20since%20the%20early-August%20drawdown.%20Hayes%20noted%