r%20moved%20to%20Panama%20City%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMcKinney%2C%20Texas%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20she%20retired%20two%20years%20later.%20From%20the%20diversity%20of%20cuisines%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20and%20access%20to%20pristine%20beaches%2C%20Lohr%20said%20life%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboquete-panama-how-to-retire-in-paradise-cost-of-living-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Central%20American%20country%20is%20superb%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPanama%20is%20just%20like%20Christmas%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Lohr%2C%2068%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20is%20one%20of%20many%20Americans%20moving%20abroad%20for%20retirement%2C%20hoping%20to%20seek%20new%20experiences%20and%20escape%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-moving-abroad-cost-of-living-too-expensive-debt-retirement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US.%20As%20of%20December%202023%2C%20there%20were%20648%2C569%20Americans%20aged%2065%20or%20older%20receiving%20Social%20Security%20benefits%20abroad%2C%20according%20to%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fpolicy%2Fdocs%2Fstatcomps%2Fsupplement%2F2024%2F5j.html%23table5.j11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20available%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Social%20Security%20Administration.%20Twenty%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fpolicy%2Fdocs%2Fstatcomps%2Fsupplement%2F2004%2F5j.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDecember%202003%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20number%20was%20352%2C340.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20Panama%20had%202%2C194%20retired%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUS%20workers%20receiving%20Social%20Security%20in%20December%202023%2C%20the%20second-highest%20number%20of%20any%20country%20in%20Central%20America%20and%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20following%20the%20Dominican%20Republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec3fdff5-ab61-4338-8cc7-0f75515454dd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreparing%20to%20move%20abroad%20requires%20research%20and%20a%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20was%20born%20in%20Dallas%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20and%20consultant%20in%20the%20US%20for%20nearly%20four%20decades.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20she%20said%20she%20became%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20culture%20in%20the%20US%2C%20particularly%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshootings-stand-your-ground-us-gun-culture-experts-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egun%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20her%20career%20background%2C%20Lohr%20said%20she%20was%20meticulous%20in%20planning%20her%20retirement%20and%20choosing%20the%20best%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20project%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20Lohr%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20spreadsheets%3B%20lots%20of%20spreadsheets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20started%20by%20researching%20the%20specifics%20of%20a%20prospective%20lifestyle%20in%20the%20regions%20she%20considered%20for%20possible%20retirement%2C%20including%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-moved-to-canada-retirement-weather-love-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espots%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20across%20the%20Caribbean.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emade%20her%20first%20%26quot%3Breconnaissance%26quot%3B%20trip%20to%20Panama%20in%20September%202019.%20She%20recommends%20that%20others%20do%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20research%20if%20they're%20considering%20retiring%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboquete-panama-how-to-retire-in-paradise-cost-of-living-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoquete%20is%20a%20popular%20destination%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20American%20retirees%20in%20Panama%2C%20but%20Lohr%20said%20it%20didn't%20fit%20her%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20little%20too%20laid%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Lohr%20said.%20%26quot%3BSince%20I'm%20an%20avid%20patron%20of%20visual%20and%20performing%20arts%2C%20I%20just%20didn't%20see%20the%20cultural%20aspects%20there%20that%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20ultimately%20settled%20on%20Panama%20City%2C%20in%20the%20Bella%20Vista%20neighborhood.%20She%20said%20what%20convinced%20her%20to%20move%20was%20the%20Cinta%20Costera%2C%20which%20is%20a%204.3-mile-long%20public%20recreation%20space%20along%20Panama%20Bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20beautiful%20garden%20spaces%2C%20bike%20lanes%2C%20city%20seating%2C%20sports%20fields%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20public%20spaces%20to%20congregate%20with%20vendors%20who%20offer%20food%20and%20drinks%20and%20souvenirs%2C%26quot%3B%20Lohr%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20beautiful%20pedestrian%20and%20marine%20promenade%20that%20takes%20you%20into%20the%20old%20town%20of%20Panama%20City.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20shows%20Panama%20City%2C%20Panama.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d1bfe01d8d2deb96b799f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22685%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaundra%20Lohr%2C%2068%2C%20moved%20to%20Panama%20City%2C%20Panama%20in%202021.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Saundra%20Lohr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20destination%20set%2C%20Lohr%20focused%20on%20lowering%20her%20expenses%20and%20preparing%20her%20finances%20for%20moving%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20have%20any%20credit%20card%20or%20consumer%20debt%20prior%20to%20my%20move%20as%20I%20had%20spent%20the%20year%20prior%20lowering%20all%20my%20financial%20obligations%2C%26quot%3B%20Lohr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20calculated%20her%20budget%20for%20moving%20abroad%20by%20adding%20up%20her%20existing%20monthly%20expenses%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eincluding%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emobile%20phone%20service%2C%20Medicare%2C%20and%20her%20estimates%20for%20cable%2C%20internet%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20electric%20bills.%20Including%20dining%20and%20entertainment%2C%20she%20said%20her%20monthly%20expenses%20amounted%20to%20about%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20receives%20about%20%242%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20Social%20Security%20and%20said%20she%20uses%20investment%20payouts%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20difference.%20She%20declined%20to%20share%20the%20specifics%20of%20those%20amounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20said%20she%20began%20investing%20at%20age%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E27%20to%20grow%20her%20wealth.%20She%20invested%20in%20various%20securities%2C%20including%20individual%20stocks%2C%20municipal%20bonds%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20date%2C%20investing%20is%20still%20a%20part%20of%20my%20strategy%20to%20remain%20financially%20secure%2C%26quot%3B%20Lohr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20move%2C%20Lohr%20hired%20an%20estate%20auctioneer%20to%20sell%20her%20belongings.%20She%20also%20sold%20or%20gave%20away%20items%20to%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20and%20neighbors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohr%20said%20using%20a%20checklist%20is%20helpful%20while%20moving%20abroad.%20She%20recommends%20splitting%20responsibilities%20into%20categories%20like%20finances%2C%20health%2C%20communications%2C%20packing%2C%20housing%2C%20and%20what%20to%20sell%20or%20donate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20homeowner%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Lohr%20said%20she%20had%20no%20interest%20in%20being%20a%20homeowner%20in%20Panama%20and%20wanted%20to%20live%20a%20simpler%20lifestyle%20than%20she%20was%20accustomed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217533b4a-d36a-4ece-ba58-0449bd611348%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20benefits%20for%20American%20retirees%20in%20Panama%3