otted%20wooden%20train%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0d9b443b5e59d16b6d3e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20French's%20father%20found%20the%20train%20car%2C%20it%20was%20decrepit%20and%20reeked%20of%20cats.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20French%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20being%20the%20train%20enthusiast%20and%20the%20visionary%20that%20my%20dad%20is%2C%20he%20offered%20to%20buy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I'll%20take%20this%20off%20your%20hands%20because%20it's%20not%20doing%20you%20any%20good%20and%20I%20love%20trains%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20figure%20something%20out%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20bought%20it%20for%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20some%20of%20the%20original%20markings%20in%20the%20paint%2C%20which%20were%20almost%20all%20gone.%20Local%20train%20buffs%20did%20some%20digging%20in%20the%20archives%2C%20and%20sure%20enough%2C%20they%20found%20the%20picture%20of%20this%20exact%20car%20the%20day%20it%20was%20built%20in%201906.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20super%20difficult%20process%20to%20move%20a%2061-foot%20train%20car%20that%20is%20in%20really%20rough%20shape.%20It's%20like%20January%2C%20early%20February%20of%202020%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20so%20muddy%20and%20snowy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cost%20us%20%2410%2C000%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20use%20semis%20and%20bulldozers%20to%20get%20it%20up%20the%20final%20hill.%20But%20at%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20we%20just%20couldn't%20go%20any%20further%2C%20so%20that%20became%20the%20resting%20place%20where%20it%20sits%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20the%20detail%20of%20the%20old%20train%20car%20and%20rotted%20wood%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0da1643b5e59d16b6d440%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrench%20said%20the%20car%20looked%20almost%20unrecognizable%20as%20a%20train%20car%20when%20he%20first%20saw%20it.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20French%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20such%20an%20ideal%20spot%20because%20it's%20on%20the%20top%20of%20this%20little%20hill%20looking%20out%20at%20this%20incredible%20little%20panorama%20of%20pristine%20Idaho%20countryside.%20You're%20just%20looking%20straight%20out%20at%20these%20rolling%20hills%20and%20canyons%20and%20trees.%20And%20it%20would've%20been%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20view%20that%20you%20would've%20seen%20from%20the%20railroad%20track%2C%20which%20is%20only%20a%20few%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20COVID-19%20started%20%E2%80%94%20but%20turning%20this%20car%20into%20an%20Airbnb%20became%20a%20perfect%20outdoors%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20order%20of%20operations%20was%20to%20build%20a%20new%20enclosure.%20It%20wasn't%20built%20to%20be%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20field%20in%20the%20elements.%20Plus%2C%20we%20wanted%20it%20to%20have%20a%20little%20porch.%20So%20my%20older%20brother%20John%20built%20this%20really%20cool%20timber%20frame%20structure%20around%20it%2C%20which%20we%20designed%2C%20that%20resembles%20the%20roof%20line%20of%20an%20original%20train%20depot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20train%20car%20being%20restored%20under%20new%20enclosure%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0da6743b5e59d16b6d451%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnce%20they%20relocated%20the%20train%20car%2C%20Isaac's%20family%20went%20to%20work%20building%20an%20enclosure%20around%20it.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20French%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restoration%20really%20was%20just%20a%20process%20of%20carefully%20sanding%2C%20stripping%20down%20inside%20and%20out%20all%20of%20the%20surface%20area%20%E2%80%94%20the%20floors%2C%20siding%2C%20interior%20paneling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20obviously%20trying%20to%20save%20everything%20we%20could.%20I%20would%20say%2095%25%20of%20the%20car%20is%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20got%20past%20that%20first%20quarter%20inch%20of%20grime%2C%20it%20was%20good%20wood%20inside.%20We%20just%20sanded%20everything%20down%20super%20carefully%20and%20then%20refinished%20it.%20The%20flooring%20to%20paneling%2C%20all%20of%20that%20is%20original.%20And%20then%2C%20we%20found%20original%20paint%20colors%20for%20the%20lime%20green%20color%20of%20the%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20combination%20car%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20used%20as%20a%20passenger%20car%2C%20a%20US%20mail%20car%2C%20and%20a%20cargo%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221358%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20bathroom%20inside%20renovated%20train%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d20d681d8d2deb96b7d61c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrench's%20family%20added%20a%20bathroom%20into%20the%20train%20car.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20French%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20the%20mail%20compartment%20as%20a%20bedroom%2C%20the%20cargo%20compartment%20for%20the%20bathroom%20and%20entryway%2C%20and%20the%20passenger%20compartment%20as%20the%20lounge%20living%20area%20and%20kitchenette.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20is%20super%20talented%20with%20interior%20design.%20She's%20very%20into%20this%20gilded%20age%2C%20antique%20style.%20And%20so%20she%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20pieces%2C%20like%20old%20chests%2C%20drawers%2C%20chairs%20and%20such%20from%20antique%20shops%20and%20estate%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20we%20worked%20with%20a%20friend%20of%20ours%20to%20do%20a%20custom%20copper%20light%20fixture%20to%20match%20pictures%20of%20the%20original%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20%24151%2C000%20all-in%2C%20including%20the%20%243%2C000%20for%20the%20car%2C%20and%20it%20took%20us%20about%20six%20months%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20living%20area%20and%20loungre%20inside%20renovated%20train%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0db9743b5e59d16b6d528%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20train%20compartments%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20lounge%20and%20living%20area.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20French%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d004c104-d963-4be3-89c8-cc4b3ef16234%5C%22%3EAirbnb%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20this%20thing%20blew%20up%20when%20we%20launched%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20booked%20up%2090%25%20occupancy%20the%20first%20year%2C%20and%20this%20quickly%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unique%20and%20profitable%20stays.%20It%20paid%20for%20itself%20in%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tricky%20thing%20is%20this%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%2C%20it's%20really%20off%20the%20beaten%20path.%20People%20have%20to%20intentionally%20carve%20out%20time%2C%20book%20a%20trip%2C%20and%20travel%20a%20long%20ways%20to%20come%20experience%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20we%20price%20it%20at%20around%20%24325%20a%20night.%20That%20seems%20like%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20based%20on%20the%20occupancy%20and%20the%20demand%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20pretty%20reasonable.%20We%20could%20technically%20raise%20the%20prices%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20plan%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20restored%20train%20car%20and%20its%20porch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0dbe243b5e59d16b6d54e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221355%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restored%20train%20car%20rests%20underneath%20a%20depot-style%20overhang%20with%20a%20large%20porch.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20French%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%20to%20come%20and%20experience%20it%20because%20there%20are%20so%20many%20people%20who%20are%20passionate%20about%20these%20restoration%20projects%20and%20specifically%20about%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20our%20history%20as%20a%20nation%20has%20to%20do%20with%20trains%2C%20yet%20their%20impact%20is%20under-appreciated.%20And%20as%20technology%20and%20transportation%20has%20evolved%2C%20trains%20have%20by%20and%20large%20been%20left%20in%20the%20dustbin%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20had%20this%20incredible%20belief%20and%20conviction%20that%20this%20car%20could%20be%20redeemed.%20And%20because%20of%20that%2C%20we%20all%20rallied%20behind%20it.%20And%20sure%20enough%2C%20it%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20see%20it%20come%20from%20such%20a%20decrepit%20and%20seemingly%20unredeemable%20condition%20and%20become%20this%20fresh%2C%20full%20of%20life%2C%20incredibly%20vibrant%20experience%20%E2%80%A6%20It's%20just%2C%20in%20every%20sense%2C%20invigorating.%20Going%20to%20that%20car%2C%20walking%20through%20it%2C%20you%20can't%20help%20but%20feel%20energy%20in%20your%20veins%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20it%20would've%20felt%20like%20back%20in%20the%20day%20to%20be%20on%20this%20same%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20thing%20was%20dead%2C%20and%20now%20it%20has%20new%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20photos%20and%20information%20about%20the%20Deary%20train%20car%2C%20you%20can%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3De123b03ca66fa29bff91da8c02b72795642826ea578453de5dfe4e9e934b9668%26postID%3D66d0acbdd5e42862f034676e%26postSlug%3Drestoration-train-car-airbnb-profitable-idaho-2024-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.airbnb.com%252Frooms%252F44613554%253Fadults%253D1%2526children%253D0%2526enable_m3_private_room%253Dtrue%2526infants%253D0%2526pets%253D0%2526search_mode%253Dregular_search%2526check_in%253D2024-08-12%2526check_out%253D2024-08-17%2526source_impression_id%