com%2Fblog%2Frental-price-data%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20research%20from%20real-estate%20site%20Zumper%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20one-bedroom%20setup%20cost%20%241%2C534%20while%20two-bedroom%20fixtures%20went%20for%20%241%2C915%2C%20which%20are%20both%20up%20by%20a%20few%20dollars%20from%20July's%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221858%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zumper%20August%20rent%20growth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0ab3943b5e59d16b6a85c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221020%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EZumper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3ERent%20has%20risen%20throughout%20this%20summer%2C%20even%20as%20a%20wave%20of%20new%20apartments%20has%20come%20online.%20There%20were%20more%20new%20US%20apartments%20available%20last%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-best-cities-for-renters-apartment-supply-rent-inflation-2024-7%5C%22%3Ethan%20at%20any%20point%20in%20the%20last%2050%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zumper%20found.%20That%20supply%20increase%20comes%20in%20response%20to%20exceptionally%20strong%20demand.%20Without%20it%2C%20renters%20would%20be%20shelling%20out%20even%20more%20money%20each%20month.%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20tenants%20aren't%20pushing%20back%20much%20against%20this%20rent%20growth%2C%20as%20rental%20vacancy%20rates%20have%20remained%20flat%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%20at%20around%206.6%25%2C%20according%20to%20Zumper.%20That%20may%20be%20because%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freddiemac.com%2Fpmms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelevated%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20still%20deterring%20homebuyers%2C%20even%20though%20they've%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mortgage%20rates%208-29%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0ab78392a3bda9f233643%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221102%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFreddie%20Mac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20era%20where%20the%20amount%20of%20new%20supply%20is%20shattering%20records%2C%20it's%20remarkable%20to%20see%20vacancy%20rates%20holding%20steady%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zumper%20CEO%20Anthemos%20Georgiades%20in%20a%20statement%20for%20the%20report.%20%26quot%3BStrong%20renter%20retention%20alongside%20our%20growing%20national%20rent%20index%20underscores%20the%20robust%20demand%20present%20in%20the%20US%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack-to-school%20season%20sends%20rent%20soaring%20in%20certain%20cities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApartment%20prices%20surged%20most%20this%20month%20in%20college%20towns%20like%20Syracuse%2C%20New%20York%3B%20New%20Haven%2C%20Connecticut%3B%20Lexington%2C%20Kentucky%3B%20Madison%2C%20Wisconsin%3B%20and%20Lincoln%2C%20Nebraska.%20Those%20towns%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20in%20the%20top%2010%20of%20year-over-year%20rent%20growth%20in%20August%2C%20are%20home%20to%20Syracuse%20University%2C%20Yale%20University%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Kentucky%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Nebraska-Lincoln%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollege%20towns%20tend%20to%20demonstrate%20stronger%20apartment%20market%20performance%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20national%20average%20since%20they%20generally%20have%20higher%20occupancy%20rates%20and%20greater%20overall%20stability%20in%20their%20rental%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Zumper%20researchers%20wrote%20in%20the%20report.%20%26quot%3BAs%20August%20marks%20this%20year's%20back-to-school%20season%2C%20the%20demand%20in%20these%20areas%20are%20likely%20reaching%20their%20peaks%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20blush%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20students%20rushing%20back%20to%20campus%20would%20cause%20demand%20to%20spike.%20However%2C%20that