d%20a%20march%20from%20the%20iconic%20Hutatma%20Chowk%20to%20Gateway%20of%20India%20in%20south%20Mumbai%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sindhudurg%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20slammed%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20for%20the%20collapse%2C%20with%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20calling%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20apology%20as%20one%20%26quot%3Bsmacking%20of%20arrogance%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20the%20episode%20was%20an%20example%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statue%20of%20the%2017th%20century%20Maratha%20warrior%20king%20at%20Rajkot%20fort%20in%20Malvan%20tehsil%2C%20some%20480%20kilometres%20from%20here%2C%20fell%20on%20August%2026.%20It%20was%20unveiled%20by%20PM%20Modi%20on%20December%204%2C%202023%2C%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Navy%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20(SP)%20supremo%20Pawar%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Thackeray%2C%20Congress%20state%20unit%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20the%20party's%20Mumbai%20head%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20began%20the%20protest%20march%20by%20laying%20wreaths%20at%20Hutatma%20Chowk%2C%20a%20memorial%20to%20those%20martyred%20in%20the%20'Samyukta%20Maharashtra'%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20at%20Gateway%20of%20India%2C%20where%20the%20protest%20march%20culminated%2C%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20you%20notice%20the%20arrogance%20in%20the%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's)%20apology%3F%20It%20smacked%20of%20arrogance.%20One%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20was%20smiling.%26quot%3B%20Asserting%20that%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20will%20never%20forgive%20the%20insult%20to%20the%20legendary%20warrior%20king%2C%20Thackeray%20cited%20the%20statue%20collapse%2C%20leakages%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20the%20new%20Parliament%20complex%20to%20mock%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bguarantees%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20what%20was%20the%20PM%20apologising%3F%20For%20the%20statue%20he%20inaugurated%20eight%20months%20ago%3F%20For%20the%20corruption%20involved%3F%20The%20MVA%20cadre%20must%20work%20together%20to%20defeat%20the%20forces%20that%20have%20insulted%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20The%20collapse%20of%20the%20statue%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20soul%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%20in%20Palghar%20on%20Friday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20is%20not%20just%20a%20name%20or%20a%20king%20but%20a%20deity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20bow%20my%20head%20at%20his%20feet%20and%20apologise%20to%20my%20deity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20protest%20march%2C%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20collapse%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj's%20statue%20in%20Sindhudurg%20is%20an%20example%20of%20corruption.%20It%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20all%20Shiv%20premis%20(followers%20of%20the%20warrior%20king).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolhapur%20Congress%20MP%20Shahu%20Chhatrapati%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20emperor%2C%20said%20the%20latter's%20dignity%20must%20be%20maintained%20at%20all%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20march%2C%20which%20began%20sometime%20after%2011am%2C%20included%20NCP%20(SP)%20Baramati%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20MLA%20Anil%20Deshmukh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bust%20of%20the%20legendary%20warrior%20king%20was%20placed%20at%20Hutatma%20Chowk%2C%20while%20those%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20protest%20march%20carried%20placards%20denouncing%20the%20statue%20collapse%20and%20shouted%20slogans%20against%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20(SP)%20chief%20Pawar%20walked%20some%20distance%20as%20part%20of%20the%20protest%20march%20before%20getting%20into%20his%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edi