%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20formed%20to%20suggest%20solutions%20and%20recommend%20measures%20after%20something%20that%20should%20never%20have%20happened.%20Welcoming%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20panel%2C%20Mammooty%20said%20police%20investigation%20is%20proceeding%20swiftly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20full%20version%20of%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20committee%20report%20is%20before%20the%20court.%20Let%20the%20police%20investigate%20honestly.%20Let%20the%20court%20decide%20the%20punishments.%20There%20is%20no%20'powerhouse'%20in%20cinema%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20actor%20said%20the%20norm%20is%20that%20the%20actors'%20organisation%20responds%20to%20such%20issues%20first.%20He%20said%20he%20waited%20this%20long%20for%20this%20very%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment%20against%20some%20top%20actors%20and%20filmmakers.%20Actors%20Jayasurya%20Sidhique%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20Maniyanpilla%20Raju%2C%20Idavela%20Babu%20and%20director%20Ranjith%20are%20among%20the%20prominent%20film%20personalities%20who%20now%20face%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20assault.%20Several%20actors%2C%20including%20Minu%20Muneer%20and%20Sonia%20Malhaar%2C%20have%20brought%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flood%20of%20allegations%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20public%20release%20of%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20last%20week.%20The%20235-page%20report%2C%20published%20after%20redacting%20names%20of%20witnesses%20and%20the%20accused%2C%20notes%20that%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20is%20controlled%20by%2010-15%20male%20producers%2C%20directors%2C%20and%20actors.%20The%20three-member%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%202017%20and%20submitted%20its%20report%20in%202019.%20The%20report%20was%20not%20made%20public%20so%20far%20due%20to%20legal%20challenges%20to%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20uproar%20has%20led%20to%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20top%20panel%20of%20Association%20of%20Malayalam%20Movie%20Artists%20or%20AMMA.%20The%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20Mohanlal%20as%20president%2C%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20moral%20responsibility%20%26quot%3Bin%20light%20of%20allegations%20made%20by%20some%20actors%20against%20some%20of%20the%20committee%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20is%20now%20probing%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20evening%2C%20Mohanlal%20said%20the%20film%20industry%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20questions%20raised%2C%20but%20the%20actors'%20association%20is%20targeted%20and%20blamed%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20part%20of%20any%20power%20group%20in%20Malayalam%20cinema%20and%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20any%20such%20group.%20I%20have%20heard%20about%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20allegations%20against%20AMMA%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAMMA%20is%20not%20an%20outfit%20with%20trade%20union%20nature.%20It%20was%20launched%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20its%20members....The%20entire%20film%20industry%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20questions%20regarding%20the%20Hema%20panel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20associations%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20AMMA%20is%20blamed%20for%20everything.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20right%20to%20crucify%20an%20outfit%20alone%20for%20all%20these%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohanlal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725178740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2F17ujb59_mammootty-instagram_625x300_18_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-is-no-power-centre-actor-mammootty-amid-mollywood-meto