ing%20the%20child%20in%20the%20described%20manner%2C%20even%20after%20being%20shown%20photos%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stated%20that%20she%20had%20over%2036%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20particularly%20with%20children%20who%20have%20special%20needs%2C%20and%20stated%20that%20her%20training%20involved%20moving%20children%20to%20a%20different%20room%20if%20they%20needed%20to%20calm%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20physical%20evidence%20and%20the%20paraeducator's%20account%2C%20deputies%20arrested%20Otero%20on%20a%20felony%20charge%20of%20child%20abuse%20without%20great%20bodily%20harm.%20The%20Volusia%20County%20School%20District%20has%20placed%20Otero%20on%20administrative%20leave%20pending%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20by%20its%20Professional%20Standards%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20has%20placed%20Otero%20on%20administrative%20leave%20and%20is%20conducting%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BVolusia%20County%20Schools%20(VCS)%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20recent%20arrest%20of%20a%20Forest%20Lake%20Elementary%20teacher.%20VCS%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20all%20of%20our%20students%20and%20is%20taking%20this%20situation%20very%20seriously.%20As%20such%2C%20our%20Professional%20Standards%20department%20is%20currently%20conducting%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20to%20determine%20the%20appropriate%20next%20steps.%20The%20teacher%20is%20currently%20on%20administrative%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725175260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcq29rl98_teacher-holding-student-captive-us-_625x300_01_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffelony-charge-for-us-teacher-who-allegedly-used-legs-to-restrain-autistic-student-6464569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2059-year-old%20teacher%20at%20Forest%20Lake%20Elementary%20in%20Volusia%20County