ancements%2C%20featuring%20improvements%20in%20Siri%2C%20systemwide%20Writing%20Tools%2C%20and%20the%20integration%20of%20ChatGPT.%20The%20iPhone%2016%20series%20will%20be%20available%20from%20September%2020%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fmobiles-tabs%2Fapple-its-glowtime-launch-event-6-apple-intelligence-features-coming-to-iphone-16-and-iphone-16-pro-models%2Farticleshow%2F112964268.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hostages%20%26quot%3BBrutally%20Murdered%26quot%3B%20Shortly%20Before%20We%20Reached%20Them%3A%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20announced%20today%20that%20it%20had%20discovered%20the%20bodies%20of%20six%20hostages%20in%20an%20underground%20tunnel%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Among%20the%20dead%20were%20dual%20citizens%2C%20including%20a%20US-Israeli%20and%20a%20Russian-Israeli.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20claimed%20that%20the%20hostages%20were%20brutally%20murdered%20by%20Hamas%20shortly%20before%20security%20forces%20could%20reach%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostages%2C%20whose%20identities%20have%20been%20confirmed%20as%20Carmel%20Gat%2C%20Eden%20Yerushalmi%2C%20Hersh%20Goldberg-Polin%2C%20Alexander%20Lobanov%2C%20Almog%20Sarusi%2C%20and%20Ori%20Danino%2C%20were%20kidnapped%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20their%20brutal%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20The%20attack%20not%20only%20triggered%20the%20ongoing%20war%20but%20also%20led%20to%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20251%20individuals%2C%20of%20whom%2097%20remain%20captive%2C%20including%2033%20who%20the%20Israeli%20army%20believes%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20hours%20ago%2C%20we%20informed%20the%20families%20that%20the%20bodies%20of%20their%20loved%20ones%20had%20been%20located%20by%20IDF%20troops%20in%20an%20underground%20