ltural%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%20is%20that%2C%20about%2030%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20paper%20is%20getting%20into%20the%20landfills%20due%20to%20being%20coated%20with%20plastic%20or%20aluminium%20and%20are%20contaminated%20with%20beverages%20that%20makes%20it%20unsuitable%20for%20recycling.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20almost%2087%20million%20tonnes%20of%20crop%20residue%20is%20burned%20annually%20in%20India%2C%20as%20per%20a%20Science%20Direct%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22B%20G%20Seetharaman%2C%20Vinay%20Kumar%20and%20Rajeeva%20Deekshit%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363693%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EB%20G%20Seetharaman%2C%20Vinay%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Rajeeva%20Deekshit%20(L-R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20this%2C%20the%20trio%20started%20Indic%20Initiatives%20in%20July%202022%20and%20have%20developed%20a%20one%20of%20its%20kind%20waste%20paper%20recycler%20that%20tackles%20the%20difficult%20to%20recycle%20paper%20cups%2C%20label%20release%20paper%2C%20tissue%20papers%20and%20tetrapaks.%20Their%20machine%20recycles%20this%20waste%20into%20pulp%20boards%2C%20which%20can%20be%20further%20used%20to%20manufacture%20paper%20and%20moulded%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncubated%20at%20NSRCEL%20(IIM%20Bangalore)%20and%20IIMV%20FIELD%20(IIM%20Visakhapatnam)%2C%20the%20startup%20is%20planning%20to%20patent%20the%20machine%E2%80%99s%20design%20and%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETackling%20the%20difficult%20to%20recycle%20plastics%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mechanical%20engineer%20from%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20Seetharaman%20also%20pursued%20research%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20in%20Bengaluru.%20After%20working%20at%20Seshasayee%20Paper%20and%20Boards%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20he%20set%20up%20his%20own%20handmade%20paper%20unit%20in%201997%2C%20called%20BG%20Boutique%20Paper%20Mills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic1-1725015497.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Recycling%20paper%20cups%20at%20source!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic1-1725015497.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic1-1725015497-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic1-1725015497-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic1-1725015497-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic1-1725015497-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363603%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERecycling%20paper%20cups%20at%20source!%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20he%20claims%20that%20they%20make%20100%20percent%20recycled%20paper%2C%20paper%20bags%20and%20stationery%20from%20jute%20and%20cotton%20waste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20a%20semi-automatic%20machine%20in%202014%20as%20a%20ready-made%20paper%20machine%20was%20not%20available%20to%20our%20size%2C%20to%20process%20say%20100-200%20kg%20per%20day.%20We%20designed%20it%20to%20make%20paper%20from%20raw%20materials%20like%20jute%20waste%2C%20leather%20waste%2C%20banana%20waste%20and%20other%20unique%20raw%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20Seetharaman%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20cost%20of%20production%20was%20high%2C%20the%20first%20lockdown%20in%202020%20caused%20a%20huge%20roadblock.%20Now%2C%20the%20engineer%20and%20scientist%20thought%20of%20developing%20a%20complete%20product%20which%20could%20recycle%20paper%20waste%20at%20source.%20He%20calls%20it%20an%20%E2%80%98end-to-end%20paper%20machine%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20lay%20in%20building%20technology%20which%20would%20recover%20clean%20plastic%2C%20by%20removing%20silicone%20coatings%2C%20hazardous%20substances%20and%20beverage%20stains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeetharaman%20had%20already%20worked%20with%20Rajeeva%20in%202017%20to%20create%20a%20technology%20that%20removed%20glassine%20from%20label%20release%20papers.Their%20technology%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359436%2Fgrow-your-microgreens-using-this-portable-chemical-free-cultivator-made-of-banana-pulp-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycle%20this%20silicone%20coated%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLabel%20release%20papers%20have%20a%20silicone%20coating%20which%20is%20hazardous%20and%20not%20recyclable.%20A%20big%20manufacturer%20had%20approached%20us%20to%20develop%20a%20technology%20to%20remove%20the%20coating%20and%20recover%20pulp.%20I%20knew%20that%20we%20could%20use%20the%20same%20technology%20for%20paper%20cups%20and%20tetra%20packs%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Seetharaman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20machine%20developed%20by%20Indic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558-300x226.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558-500x376.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558-768x578.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558-1536x1156.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Findic2-min-1725015558-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363604%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221204%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20machine%20developed%20by%20Indic%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETetra%20packs%20too%20come%20coated%20with%20plastic%20or%20aluminium%20and%20are%20usually%20contaminated%20with%20beverages%2C%20tissue%20paper%2C%20and%20label%20release%20paper.%20Due%20to%20these%20complications%2C%20tetra%20packs%20and%20paper%20cups%20are%20not%20generally%20recycled%2C%20opines%20Seetharaman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20they%20are%20getting%20recycled%20efficiently%20because%20of%20their%20layers%20of%20plastic%20and%20aluminium.%20Separation%20of%20these%20layers%20is%20not%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20grants%20and%20awards%20after%20winning%20ELEVATE%20Karnataka%202023%20and%20Nidhi%20Prayas%202023%2C%20they%20built%20a%20pilot%20plant%20in%20Chikkamagaluru%2C%20where%20they%20were%20able%20to%20efficiently%20separate%20plastic%20from%20the%20paper%20cups%20and%20silicone%20gum%20from%20silicone%20coated%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20a%20proof%20of%20concept%20at%20the%20minimum%20viable%20product%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20unit%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecover%20clean%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20aluminium%20coatings%20for%20reuse%2C%20recover%20hazardous%20ink%20waste%20for%20reuse%20and%20upcycled%20fibrous%20agricultural%20wastes%20to%20create%20paper%20pulp%20that%20can%20be%20made%20into%20high-strength%20paper%20used%20for%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vinay%2C%20Founder%20of%20Indic%20Initiatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20chartered%20accountant%20by%20education%2C%20Vinay%20is%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%20who%20started%20Indic%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20indigenous%20innovations%20that%20will%20benefit%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20machine%20works%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FTransformation-gif-1-1725015809.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363610%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20paper%20cups%2C%20tetra%20packs%20or%20tissues%20are%20received%2C%20they%20are%20manually%20put%20inside%20the%20recycling%20machine.%20The%20components%20go%20through%20a%20three-stage%20process.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20tetra%20packs%2C%20the%20machine%20uses%20a%20chemical%20suspension%20to%20separate%20it%20into%20aluminium%2C%20plastic%20and%20pulp.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20paper%20cups%2C%20it%20is%20separated%20into%20plastic%20and%20pulp.%20The%20pulp%20is%20then%20converted%20into%20pulp%20boards%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Seetharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20pulp%20boards%20are%20sold%20as%20raw%20materials%20for%20paper%20making%20or%20making%20moulded%20products.%20The%20aluminium%20and%20paper%20waste%20is%20sorted%20separately%20and%20given%20to%20recyclers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajeeva%20states%20that%20they%20developed%20an%20eco-friendly%20solution%20which%20separates%20these%20aluminium%2C%20silicone%20and%20plastic%20from%20tetra%20packs%20and%20paper%20cups%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20unique%20aspect%20about%20the%20machine%2C%20says%20Seetharaman%2C%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20effluents%20released%20by%20the%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20in%20the%20paper%20and%20agriculture%20machines%2C%20we%20have%20ensured%20that%20there%20is%20no%20effluent%20released.%20Even%20in%20the%20case%20of%20banana%20waste%2C%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20extracting%20the%20sap%20and%20using%20it%20as%20a%20liquid%20fertiliser.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20zero%20liquid%20discharge%20arrangement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7155481472135520257%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20machine%20is%20designed%20for%20villages%2C%20malls%2C%20airports%20and%20more.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20recycling%2050%20kg%20of%20paper%20waste%20per%20day%2C%20which%20can%20be%