.com%2Freel%2FC-7cVCcIMl6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20pursuing%20Company%20Secretaryship%20in%202013%2C%20he%20found%20that%20his%20heart%20was%20in%20cooking%20and%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20from%20childhood%2C%20I%20always%20had%20this%20dream%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353745%2Fakash-muralidharan-masterchef-tamil-winner-vizha-medai-south-indian-food-adhd-ravioli-rasam-pongal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20my%20cookery%20show%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%2C%20how%20and%20where%3B%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20how%20to%20go%20about%20it.%20Then%20it%20struck%20me%2C%20starting%20my%20channel%20on%20YouTube%20would%20be%20a%20great%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nikunj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20by%20cooking%20authentic%20Kathiyawadi%20dishes%20using%20fresh%20and%20local%20ingredients%20from%20the%20farm.%20What%20attracts%20viewers%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20takes%20us%20through%20the%20process%20of%20sourcing%20the%20ingredients%20and%20cooks%20them%20on%20the%20farm%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20channel%20%E2%80%98Crazy%20For%20Indian%20Food%E2%80%99%20has%20over%205.9%20lakh%20subscribers%2C%20with%20the%20most%20popular%20video%20having%20a%20whopping%209.1%20million%20views!%20Besides%20cooking%20food%2C%20he%20also%20reviews%20popular%20street%20food%20joints%20and%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20one%20channel%20in%202013%2C%20he%20has%20expanded%20to%20running%20a%20network%20called%20Foodon%20TV%2C%20which%20runs%20six%20channels%20and%20four%20websites%20in%20six%20languages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20rose%20to%20fame%2C%20he%20also%20battled%20with%20personal%20probl