0the%20first%20%E2%80%98AI%20model%E2%80%99%20of%20our%20brain%20is%20written%20without%20our%20consent.%20Children%20just%20become%20what%20they%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20emphatically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20started%20sharing%20his%20understanding%20of%20parenting%20on%20social%20media%20and%20why%20children%20behave%20a%20certain%20way.%20With%20parents%20leading%20busy%20lives%2C%20Harpreet%20wishes%20to%20help%20them%20through%20his%20five-minute%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Parents%2C%20observe%20from%20a%20distance%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20with%20a%20manual.%20Earlier%2C%20people%20would%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Bacche%20aise%20hi%20bade%20ho%20jayenge%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333887%2Fsangopita-shelter-home-disabled-children-cerebral-palsy-autism-adhd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChildren%20grow%20up%20automatically%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Yes%2C%20but%20will%20they%20grow%20up%20properly%3F%20That%20is%20why%20I%20want%20parents%20to%20observe%20their%20children.%20Think%20about%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethey%20are%20doing%20what%20they%20are%20doing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20830px)%20100vw%2C%20830px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22830%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harpreet%20found%20his%20calling%20after%2040%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013.jpeg%20830w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-219