-4-1724335515-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-4-1724335515-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20an%20attempt%20at%20sustainable%20living%20and%20responsible%20tourism.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20day%2C%20Deka%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20spray%20any%20chemicals%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20land.%20It%20is%20six%20years%20and%20his%20commitment%20still%20holds%20true.%20But%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20he%20cautions.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20make%20mistakes%20and%20you%20will%20learn%20from%20them%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20you%20might%20not%20get%20it%20right.%20But%20with%20each%20season%2C%20you%20will%20learn%20to%20refine%20your%20techniques%20and%20to%20read%20your%20plants%20and%20understand%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20making%20inferences%20on%20plant%20health%20when%20he%20begins%20spotting%20signs%20of%20disease%20cropping%20up.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20that%20I%20have%20sent%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20plant%20to%20the%20agricultural%20development%20officer%20explaining%20the%20symptoms.%20They%20responded%20saying%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20fungal%20infection%20and%20that%20I%20should%20resort%20to%20a%20particular%20chemical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20like%20these%2C%20when%20Deka%20responds%20by%20saying%20he%20does%20not%20use%20chemicals%20on%20his%20plants%2C%20the%20line%20remains%20silent%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20This%20journey%20of%20odds%20would%20deter%20him%20you%E2%80%99d%20think.%20But%20i