nts%20on%20scooters%20transformed%20into%20a%20dedicated%20effort%20as%20more%20caterers%20joined%20to%20support%20his%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20Somnath%20had%20established%20a%20more%20formal%20setup%20called%20%E2%80%98Dihadi%20Kitchen%E2%80%99%2C%20involving%20a%20small%20unit%20with%20hired%20cooks.%20He%20expanded%20the%20operations%20to%20serve%20more%20than%20just%20leftover%20food%20but%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266374%2Fcommunity-kitchens-help-marginalised-women-transgenders-skill-training-golden-heart-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreshly%20prepared%20meals%20%3C%2Fa%3Efocusing%20on%20hygiene%20and%20cleanliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Somnath%20started%20%E2%80%98Dihadi%20Kitchen%E2%80%99%20in%20Lucknow%20to%20provide%20regular%2C%20hygienic%20meals%20to%20labourers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FDihadi-kitchen-2-1724331221-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESomnath%20started%20%E2%80%98Dihadi%20Kitchen%E2%80%99%20in%20Lucknow%20to%20prov